Package: parseAtekst
Title: Parse and import articles bundled in .txt-files downloaded from ATEKST
Version: 1.2
Authors@R: person("Mikael Poul", "Johannesson", email = "mikajoh@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This R-package provides functions for extracting articles (with metadata) from .txt-files downloaded from ATEKST and import them into R. They return a data frame with the headline, paper, date and time of publication, mode (net vs print), url and text of each news article.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), foreach, iterators, doParallel, parallel
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: true
